    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "A new mealybug in the genus Pseudococcus Westwood (Hemiptera: Coccomorpha: Pseudococcidae) from North America, with a key to species of Pseudococcus from the New World" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271263>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271264>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271265> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271263>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Pseudococcus variabilis sp. n. Macroscopic appearance. 1 a. Adult female, ovisac wax, eggs and juveniles on Agave sp. leaf from Nursery in Irwindale, California, U. S. A. Photograph: Gevork Arakelian. 1 b. Agave sp. plant at the San Diego Zoo in California, U. S. A., with infestation of Pseudococcus variabilis sp. n. near base and on underside of lower leaves. Photograph: Tracy Ellis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/271263/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271264>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Pseudococcus variabilis sp. n. Holotype female, U. S. A., California, San Diego Co., on Agave sp., deposited at CSCA. Enlargements of structures are not drawn to scale. l: measurement of labium length; t: measurement of tentorium length." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/271264/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.271265>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Pseudococcus variabilis sp. n. Male paratype, U. S. A., California, San Diego Co., on Agave sp., deposited at CSCA. Enlargements of structures are not drawn to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/271265/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

